### Get available leave types
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/types

### Get available leave statuses
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/statuses

### Get my leave balance
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/balance/1
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/balance/1?year=2024

### Apply for leave
POST http://localhost:3000/api/leave/apply/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "CASUAL",
  "fromDate": "2024-12-20",
  "toDate": "2024-12-22",
  "reason": "Family function",
  "halfDay": false,
  "emergency": false
}

### Get my leave requests
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/my/1
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/my/1?status=PENDING&year=2024&page=1&limit=10

### Get my leave statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/stats/1
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/stats/1?year=2024

### Cancel my leave request
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/leave/cancel/1/1

### Get all leave requests (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/admin/all
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/admin/all?status=PENDING&year=2024&page=1&limit=10

### Get users for leave management
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/admin/users

### Get single leave request
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/admin/1

### Update leave status (approve/reject)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/leave/admin/status/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approverId": 2,
  "status": "APPROVED",
  "comments": "Approved as per company policy"
}

### Get admin leave statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/admin/stats
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/admin/stats?year=2024

### Get leave calendar
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/calendar/2024/12
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leave/calendar/2024/12?userId=1